			<p><i>This article is intended to focus on the condition in adults. See also main article, <a href="/wiki/Attention-deficit_hyperactivity_disorder" title="Attention-deficit hyperactivity disorder">Attention-deficit hyperactivity disorder</a>.</i></p>
