<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Adult_attention-deficit_disorder&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.nimh.nih.gov/publicat/adhd.cfm" class="external text" title="http://www.nimh.nih.gov/publicat/adhd.cfm" rel="nofollow">National Institute for Mental Health official website</a></li>
